@type TraitDef
@kind struct
@fields
  name: str — Trait name
  method_names: [str] — Required method names (1-based)
  parent_traits: [str] — Supertrait names (1-based)
  assoc_type_names: [str] — Associated type names (1-based)
  default_starts: [i64] — Token start for default method bodies (0 = no default)
  default_ends: [i64] — Token end for default method bodies
@purpose Defines a trait's interface: required methods, supertraits, associated types, and default method body locations. Used for trait bound checking and impl validation.
@invariants All arrays are 1-based with sentinels at index 0. default_starts/default_ends are parallel to method_names.
