  type_name: str — Type implementing the trait
  assoc_type_names: [str] — Associated type names (1-based)
  assoc_type_values: [str] — Associated type concrete values (parallel to assoc_type_names)
@purpose Records that a specific type implements a specific trait. Used for operator trait validation (e.g., does i64 implement Add?) and generic trait bound checking.
