@type TraitRegistry
@kind struct
@fields
  trait_defs: [TraitDef] — All trait definitions (1-based)
  impl_defs: [ImplDef] — All trait implementations (1-based)
@purpose Stores all trait definitions and their implementations. Initialized with built-in traits (Eq, Ord, Hash, Add, Sub, Mul, Div, Mod, Numeric, Clone, Debug, Display, Convert, TryConvert, Drop, Send, Share, error categories) and primitive type impls via populate_builtins.
@invariants All arrays are 1-based with sentinels at index 0. Built-in traits and primitive impls are always present after populate_builtins.
