@type CE
@kind struct
@fields
  c: Checker — Updated checker state
  type_id: i64 — Type of checked expression
@purpose Return type for all expression-checking functions. Bundles the updated Checker state with the inferred type ID of the expression. This is the checker's equivalent of a (state, value) pair from a state monad.
@notes Every _check_* function that processes an expression returns CE. The caller must use ce.c (updated checker) for subsequent operations and ce.type_id for the expression's type.
@source_file src/checker/checker.aria
@source_line 42

