@type CheckResult
@kind struct
@fields
  store: TypeStore — Final type store with all discovered types
  registry: TypeRegistry — Final type/function registry with all signatures and monomorphizations
  treg: TraitRegistry — Final trait registry with all trait definitions and implementations
  diagnostics: DiagnosticBag — All check diagnostics (errors and warnings)
@purpose Output of the check() function. Contains everything the lowerer and codegen need: the complete type store, all struct/function definitions, trait information, and any diagnostic messages.
@workflow Consumed by the lowerer (src/lowerer/) to generate IR, and by codegen for emitting native code. The diagnostics are rendered to the user if any errors are present.
