@fn types_equal
@sig (store: TypeStore, a: i64, b: i64) -> bool
@purpose Structural type equality check. Returns true if both IDs reference the same type. For simple types, ID equality suffices. For compound types (Array, Result, Optional, Tuple), recurses into sub-types. Named types compare by name string.
